<definition-item date-revised="2024-01-01"><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">A21B</classification-symbol><definition-title>BAKERS&apos; OVENS; MACHINES OR EQUIPMENT FOR BAKING  (domestic baking equipment <class-ref scheme="cpc">A47J37/00</class-ref>)</definition-title><definition-statement><section-title>Definition statement</section-title><section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body">Industrial baker&apos;s ovens for baking food products;</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body">Parts or accessories for such ovens, e.g. baker&apos;s peels and baking forms, tins, sheets or boards used in such ovens;</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body">Baking apparatuses for specials goods, e.g. waffles, cups, cones, pancakes, doughnuts;</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body">Baking plants and baking apparatuses in combination with mixing or kneading devices.</paragraph-text></section-body></definition-statement><references><section-title>References</section-title><limiting-references><section-title>Limiting references</section-title><section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place does not cover:</paragraph-text><table>
